由於來自敘利亞的移民較易獲批難民身份，引起一些非敘利亞人利用被竊或偽造的敘利亞護照冒充敘利亞人申請庇護。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/sep/08/growing-concern-over-trade-in-fake-and-stolen-syrian-passports |title=Concern over burgeoning trade in fake and stolen Syrian passports |publisher=The Guardian |date=2015-09-08 |accessdate=2015-09-09 |archive-date=2021-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210327114755/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/sep/08/growing-concern-over-trade-in-fake-and-stolen-syrian-passports |dead-url=no }}</ref>敘利亞政府在2015年放寬在境外申請護照的規限，獲授權的駐外國大使館不需要把申請文件呈交國內政府部門審核即可發出護照，新措施被指有可能導致非敘利亞人更易獲取真的敘利亞護照。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3230384/Fears-terrorists-economic-migrants-obtaining-Syrian-passports-checks-bid-reach-Europe-10-000-handed-embassy-Jordan-just-one-month.html |title=Migrants could be getting Syrian passports with few checks in their bid to reach Europe |work=Daily Mail Online |date=2015-09-11 |accessdate=2015-09-14 |archive-date=2020-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204160450/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3230384/Fears-terrorists-economic-migrants-obtaining-Syrian-passports-checks-bid-reach-Europe-10-000-handed-embassy-Jordan-just-one-month.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>一些穆斯林移民為求增加獲批難民身份的機會，到達歐洲後[[塔基亞|改信]]基督教，然後以「被遣返則可能遭受宗教迫害」作為尋求庇護的理由。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1209432-20150904.htm |title=信奉伊斯蘭教難民 部分抵歐洲後改信基督 |publisher=香港電台 |date=2015-09-04}}</ref>

在2015年4月至6月期間，抵達歐盟國家申請庇護的移民有213,000人，當中只有44,000人來自敘利亞，而27,000人來自阿富汗，17,700人來自沒有戰亂的阿爾巴尼亞，13,900人來自伊拉克。單在2015年8月一個月內，有156,000名非正規移民抵達歐洲。<ref name=mail3240010>{{Cite news |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3240010/Number-refugees-arriving-Europe-soars-85-year-just-one-five-war-torn-Syria.html |title=Four out of five migrants are NOT from Syria: EU figures expose the 'lie' |work=Daily Mail Online |date=2015-09-18 |accessdate=2015-09-20 |archive-date=2021-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324234051/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3240010/Number-refugees-arriving-Europe-soars-85-year-just-one-five-war-torn-Syria.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在2015年，[[阿富汗|阿富汗]]人到歐洲申請庇護的人數急升，至10月已有12.4萬阿富汗人申請庇護，然而當中向德國申請庇護者接近一半人因為被認定不屬政治難民而被拒絕給予庇護。<ref name=apple20151028>{{Cite news |url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20151028/19349940 |title=人潮前仆後繼　政策大逆轉 德局部遣返阿富汗難民 |work=蘋果日報 |location=香港 |date=2015-10-28 |accessdate=2015-10-29 |archive-date=2016-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161006154853/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20151028/19349940 |dead-url=no }}</ref>德國內政部長[[托马斯·德梅齐埃|托马斯·德梅齐埃]]認為大批阿富汗中產階層來到德國申請庇護是不能接受，認為他們應該留在阿富汗建設國家。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.dw.com/en/germany-to-send-afghan-refugees-back/a-18812173 |title=Germany to send Afghan refugees back |publisher=德國之聲 |date=2015-10-28 |accessdate=2016-10-06 |archive-date=2021-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214171740/https://www.dw.com/en/germany-to-send-afghan-refugees-back/a-18812173 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

