ad-url=no }}</ref>同月瑞典一個無成人陪伴青少年尋求庇護者收容中心有一名女職員被人用刀刺斃，一名住在該中心的15歲尋求庇護者疑犯被捕。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3416343/Sweden-asylum-worker-22-stabbed-death-frenzied-attack-CHILD-migrant-centre-refugee-boy-15-arrested-murder.html |title=Sweden's Alexandra Mezher stabbed to death at CHILD migrant centre |work=Daily Mail Online |date=2016-01-26 |accessdate=2016-01-26 |archive-date=2021-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210310095614/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3416343/Sweden-asylum-worker-22-stabbed-death-frenzied-attack-CHILD-migrant-centre-refugee-boy-15-arrested-murder.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

